content: Working on a custom fine-tuning pipeline for Xander. It's about adapting the model for personal assistant use. Lots of trial and error.
Went to an AI ethics workshop. It's crucial to consider the implications of AI like Xander. Ethics will guide his development.
Xander's first NFT character sketch is done. It's simple, but it's a start. Excited to see where this visual aspect takes us.
